Create a Patient#index page that displays a link to each patient's 
show page and the total number of appointments they have.

<h1> Patient Index Page </h1>

<ul>
    <% @patients.each do |p| %>
        <li> 
            <%= link_to p.name, patient_path(p)%> <%= p.appointments.count %> <% if p.appointments.count == 1 %> appointment <%else%> appointments <%end%>
        </li>
    <%end%>
</ul>        
